            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                B<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Adtic<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> Leae qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> ante tenpus <note>sic</note> sicut <lb n="3"/>arbor deruit inm<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>tura poma <lb n="4"/>reliquid <note>sic</note> quorum <supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>ec eloquentia <lb n="5"/>potuit cognosc<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>re sic subito <lb n="6"/>natur<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> red<expan><ex>d</ex><abbr>it</abbr></expan> <supplied reason="lost">de</supplied>bitum <lb n="7"/>quae <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> cum virginio suo <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> X <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>mens</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> II exiit de s<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ec</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXIIII <lb n="9"/>contra votum posuit depo<lb break="no" n="10"/>sita die pri<expan><ex>di</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Idus Maias
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Namensform Adtica, eine Variante von Attica, in ILCV 3704 belegt. (B): AE, Z. 1: B(onae); Calderini, Z. 2: Adtictle; Z. 3: inmatura; Z. 4: de eloquentia; Z. 5: cognoscere; Z. 8: [---] de sec(ulo); Z. 10: pr(id)ie; M(a)ias.</p>
